== Mentor Learning Path

Mentors play a critical role in helping podlings learn the Apache Way.  
This path introduces the core responsibilities and provides exercises to practice.

[.small]
*Key:* 📘 Guide 🖥️ Slide Deck 🎞️ Video 🧩 Quiz 🧠 Practice / Scenario

== Steps

1. 📘 **Read:** link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Incubator+Mentor+Quick+Start+Guide[Mentor Quick Start Guide] — fast orientation for new mentors  
2. 📘 **Read:** link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Mentor+Onboarding[Mentor Onboarding] — detailed overview of mentor responsibilities and expectations  
3. 🎞️ **Watch:** link:https://youtu.be/kdxCJY97vZA[Mentor Onboarding] — video of Mentor Onboarding presentation  
4. 🧩 **Quiz:** link:https://canvas.instructure.com/enroll/JHL8BM[ASF Mentor Onboarding Quiz]  
5. 🧠 **Practice:** link:https://canvas.instructure.com/enroll/GXPFY3[Mentor Scenarios Training]  
6. 📘 **Read:** link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Best+Practices+for+Mentors[Best Practices for Mentors] — real-world mentoring examples and scenarios  
7. 📘 **Read:** link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Incubator+Case+Studies[Incubator Case Studies] — lessons learned from past podlings  
8. 📘 **Read:** link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Mentors+Tough+Conversation+Guide[Mentors’ Tough Conversation Guide] — approaches for handling challenging situations  

